ealing with fever and abdominal pain for three weeks.","dimension":6,"group":5,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.50184,0.241,0.083345,0.049438,0.033379,0.023864,0.018198,0.014143,0.01173,0.010088,0.0078011,0.0051729],"unified_progress":[0.30335,0.3535,0.01085,0.078489,0.059632,0.047737,0.038027,0.031357,0.025701,0.020859,0.017441,0.013057]},{"section":2,"text":"That's quite a while, so it sounds like something that's been brewing for a bit.","dimension":0,"group":7,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.13992,0.1941,0.15746,0.12217,0.096951,0.077103,0.060587,0.045441,0.037994,0.029967,0.023298,0.014992],"unified_progress":[0.10627,0.15068,0.11844,0.10697,0.11077,0.092613,0.079403,0.066083,0.055762,0.0464,0.038604,0.028004]},{"section":3,"text":"Now he suddenly gets really bad abdominal pain and starts vomiting a lot.","dimension":6,"group":5,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.17535,0.17476,0.13317,0.10402,0.086924,0.073151,0.062193,0.051967,0.045217,0.040687,0.032202,0.020354],"unified_progress":[0.1093,0.13695,0.11222,0.10461,0.0926,0.087291,0.076826,0.07486,0.065215,0.055702,0.047565,0.03686]},{"section":4,"text":"That's pretty intense and suggests something serious might be going on.","dimension":0,"group":7,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.075135,0.14182,0.14215,0.12878,0.11166,0.096405,0.08115,0.064255,0.056096,0.045404,0.035416,0.021725],"unified_progress":[0.061647,0.10577,0.11018,0.11074,0.11234,0.099148,0.095009,0.080796,0.072102,0.061813,0.052621,0.037832]},{"section":5,"text":"The X-ray shows air under the diaphragm.","dimension":9,"group":1,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.044902,0.08669,0.11153,0.131,0.13134,0.12033,0.10315,0.082216,0.066057,0.0568,0.041743,0.024235],"unified_progress":[0.049534,0.084705,0.098743,0.10926,0.11041,0.10428,0.096989,0.088406,0.086708,0.068717,0.056671,0.045581]},{"section":6,"text":"Hmm, that usually means there's some kind of perforation or leak in the gastrointestinal tract.","dimension